Hollywood duo Goldie Hawn and Kurt Russell have been together for a whopping 36 years, but they’ve yet to make it down the aisle!

The pair doesn’t call themselves husband and wife, but that doesn’t mean their three-decade-long relationship hasn’t had its fair share of ups and downs! In fact, The National ENQUIRER has dug up some of Goldie and Kurt’s darkest relationship secrets!

